race.description: Sportsbet Get On Extra Bm62 Handicap
race.comment: SINISTER SAUCE (11) is racing very well this time in, winning 2/4 and placing in the others. She put up a new peak level last time winning at Werribee by 1.5 lengths in a BM56. This is a touch harder but she sets up for every chance to repeat the dose. FOX APPEAL (1) is going well and comes back in grade for this with claims. SOTOMAYOR (15) won well as favourite last start and only looks to have to repeat that effort to be right in the finish again. GEE TEE (14) will likely get back from the wide draw, but should be strong late with improvement expected second up.
